Package fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.components

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Broker
    A Broker is the heart of a PubSub component, in fact The PubSub class delegate all its operations to the Broker class.
    CBuilder<T extends CBuilder<T>>
    A CBuilder class represents an implementation of the builder design pattern.
    HandlerExecutor
    A HandlerExecutor is an abstraction of handling the requests that a broker will receive.
    Publisher
    A Publisher component handles publishing messages to the PubSub.
    Publisher.Builder
    The Builder class of this Publisher component.
    PublisherExecutor
    The PublisherExecutor handles message publishing for the Broker.
    PubSub
    A PubSub is the heart of the publication/subscription system.
    PubSub.Builder
    The Builder class of this PubSub component.
    PubSubNode
    A PubSubNode component acts like a local PubSub component for each host, and should only used in Distributed CVM.
    PubSubNode.Builder
    The Builder class of this PubSubNode component.
    Subscriber
    A Subscriber component handles subscriber related requests and send them to the PubSub.
    Subscriber.Builder
    The Builder class of this Subscriber component.
    SubscriberExecutor
    The SubscriberExecutor handles subscriber related requests for the Broker.
